				<br><blockquote><hr>renaden wrote:<br><div></div><br>
<blockquote>
<hr>
Ophidion_Vaz wrote:<br>Probably because they had 14 clerics and
about 4 total dps toons. Our dps kicks like a bull with icy hot on his
